# Design System and Theme

## Design Philosophy

WalletPulse follows enterprise-grade, human-centered design principles:
- Clean, spacious layouts with generous whitespace
- Smooth micro-interactions on every touchable element
- Skeleton loading states (never blank screens)
- Haptic feedback on important actions
- Consistent visual hierarchy through typography scale
- Card-based layouts with subtle shadows and rounded corners
- Bottom sheet modals instead of full-screen overlays for quick actions

