## Spacing Scale (multiples of 4)

`xs: 4, sm: 8, md: 12, base: 16, lg: 20, xl: 24, 2xl: 32, 3xl: 40, 4xl: 48, 5xl: 64`

## Typography Scale

`caption: 11, footnote: 13, body: 15, callout: 16, headline: 17, title3: 20, title2: 22, title1: 28, largeTitle: 34`

## Border Radius

`xs: 6, sm: 8, md: 12, lg: 16, xl: 20, 2xl: 24, full: 9999`

## Shadow Elevation

```ts
export const shadows = {
  sm: { shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 1 }, shadowOpacity: 0.04, shadowRadius: 4, elevation: 1 },
  md: { shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 }, shadowOpacity: 0.06, shadowRadius: 8, elevation: 3 },
  lg: { shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 4 }, shadowOpacity: 0.08, shadowRadius: 16, elevation: 6 },
};
```

## Rules

- Never hardcode colors; always reference theme tokens
- Use `useTheme()` hook to access current theme
- Always use `StyleSheet.create()` at file bottom
- Dark/light mode follows system preference via `useColorScheme()`
- Every data screen must have: skeleton, empty, error, and loaded states
- Cards use `surface` background with `md` shadow and `lg` border radius
- Interactive elements use `react-native-reanimated` for 60fps animations
- Haptic feedback via `react-native-haptic-feedback` on: button press, swipe action, toggle, pull-to-refresh
